org.ljtoolkit.client
Class LJClientCmdLine

java.lang.Object
  org.ljtoolkit.client.LJClientCmdLine

public class LJClientCmdLine
extends java.lang.Object

The purpose of this class is to aid in the command line parsing for the LJClient class. This class will process the command line arguments supplied by the user of LJClient and will provide the values entered. If any of the required command line arguments are missing this class will display the help message.

Troy Bourdon
